title: The Creature From Jekyll Island - G. Edward Griffin
description:
DISCLAIMER: G. Edward Griffin does not implicate Jews which means he is either in on it, afraid, or just plain stupid. Either way, he has some very useful information.

The Creature From Jekyll Island.mp3

Audio recording of G Edward Griffin giving a presentation in Los Angeles on his book on the Federal Reserve, The Creature From Jekyll Island. Recorded by Reality Zone, and made freely available. Duration: 1hr 13min.
